metadata.name: Psychedelic Heaven
metadata.description:
My second artwork within the Trinity of Venus series. In this rendition, we see our heroine trying to be forced into a realm where unhealthy addictions and toxicity rule true.

Having a solid voice and independence are essential to flourish both as individuals and as a community. Let no one in your life dictate what you truly desire, and let your passions roam free.

They will permeate through the hearts of all beings that are lucky enough to know the embrace of the fabric of love. And what better love than that of a woman of complex and lasting beauty?

Soar into the skies, and you shall be welcome with the warm grasp of the bright heavens.
